== 製作 ==
2019年10月7日，[[夢工廠動畫公司|夢工廠動畫公司]]宣佈正在製作改編自電視動畫劇集《{{le|小馬王：自由奔馳|Spirit Riding Free}}》的電影，該片同時也是2002年電影《[[小馬王|小馬王]]》的續集，由伊萊恩·博根執導，《小馬王：自由奔馳》的製作人{{le|奧莉·瓦靈頓|Aury Wallington}}擔任編劇<ref name="SRFfilm">{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/dreamworks-animation-2021-releases-spirit-riding-free-the-bad-guys-1202753767/|title=DreamWorks Animation & Universal To Release 'Spirit Riding Free' & 'The Bad Guys' In 2021|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=2019-10-07|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2019-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205053635/https://deadline.com/2019/10/dreamworks-animation-2021-releases-spirit-riding-free-the-bad-guys-1202753767/|archive-date=2019-12-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年3月12日，宣佈[[伊莎貝拉·莫塞德|伊莎貝拉·莫塞德]]、{{le|瑪賽·馬汀|Marsai Martin}}、[[麥肯娜·葛瑞絲|麥肯娜·葛瑞絲]]、[[茱莉安·摩爾|茱莉安·摩爾]]、[[傑克·葛倫霍|傑克·葛倫霍]]、[[華頓·哥金斯|華頓·哥金斯]]、[[艾莎·岡薩雷|艾莎·岡薩雷]]和[[安德雷·布勞爾|安德雷·布勞爾]]加盟配音陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=https://people.com/movies/spirit-untamed-first-look-hear-taylor-swifts-re-recorded-wildest-dreams-taylors-version-in-trailer/|title=Spirit Untamed First Look! Hear Taylor Swift's Re-Recorded 'Wildest Dreams'|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|date=2021-03-12|last=Fernández|first=Alexia|access-date=2021-03-12|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312171542/https://people.com/movies/spirit-untamed-first-look-hear-taylor-swifts-re-recorded-wildest-dreams-taylors-version-in-trailer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《奔馳吧！小馬王》由環球影業於2021年6月4日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web |last1=D'Alessandro |first1=Anthony |title=Jennifer Lopez Romantic Comedy 'Marry Me' Heads To Summer |url=https://deadline.com/2020/11/jennifer-lopez-marry-me-maluma-movie-summer-2021-release-date-spirit-untamed-june-release-1234612262/ |access-date=2020-11-10 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |date=2020-11-10 |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110180056/https://deadline.com/2020/11/jennifer-lopez-marry-me-maluma-movie-summer-2021-release-date-spirit-untamed-june-release-1234612262/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此前，上映日期曾定於2021年5月14日<ref name="SRFfilm" />。
=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據115條評論，本片獲得49%的新鮮度，平均得分5.5／10，觀眾投票獲得95%的分數，平均得分為4.6／5<ref>{{Cite Rotten Tomatoes|title=Spirit Untamed|id=spirit_untamed|type=movie|access-date=2021-06-04}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得49分<ref>{{Cite Metacritic|id=spirit-untamed|type=movie|title=Spirit Untamed|access-date=2021-06-04}}</ref>。

